    <h2>Welcome to ASPIRE INTERNATIONAL SCHOOL</h2>
    ASPIRE INTERNATIONAL SCHOOL, an initiative of the Sar-la Education Trust, offers a new age delivery of education that promotes learning without compromising on inculcating a spirit of competition. The school delivers an International (IGCSE)  syllabus, the 1st International School in Nagpur with the IGCSE syllabus. It is delivered in a student friendly manner with focus on enhancing understanding and retention. In academic year 2019-2020, the school offers admissions for Nursery to Grade 10 and more grades will be added each year.

Aspire believes that every student is an individual guided by a unique personality and hence the school offers an education system that weaves academic and artistic excellence with social engagement and moral awareness. In addition to academics, activities aimed at developing the overall personality of the student are offered as part of the curriculum. Various sports and Extra Curricular activities and competitions, such as Art, Music, Dance, Debate and Elocution are planned to promote Public speaking skills and nurture creative expression.

The beautiful 9-acre campus in Nagpur offers facilities for various sports including – both Outdoor: Basketball, Football, Throwball, Volleyball, Athletics and Cricket; and Indoor: Badminton, Table tennis and Gymnastics.

Aspire School is a student-centered community with a dedicated and caring faculty, small classes and an education that recognizes each student as an individual. Aspire encourages initiative and self-direction in students as they grow and thus creates young adults dedicated to the pursuit of ongoing learning and eager to contribute positively to the global society of the 21st century.

